se of constructible sets, Saharon Shelah (1974) has shown that a famous ope=
n problem in abelian group theory (Whitehead=E2=80=99s Problem) is undecida=
ble in ZFC.</p>
<p>As suggested earlier, since essentially all mathematical concepts can be=
